    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. This car is in truly incredible shape\u2014it honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been babied since day one, kept in a climate-controlled garage, and there isn't a single scratch or smudge to be found. It runs like a dream and still has that wonderful new-car smell. I'm sad to see it go, but I'd love for it to go to a home where it'll be just as cherished. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
