    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in museum-quality condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp with a razor-sharp 8,000 RPM redline via six individual throttle bodies. The high-pressure Double VANOS system has been meticulously overhauled, and the rod bearings were replaced preventatively with WPC-treated units. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis is structurally flawless, featuring a verified and reinforced rear subframe. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the paint depth remains consistent across all panels, and the suspension retains its factory-spec damping and lateral stiffness. A truly unmolested, turn-key masterpiece for the discerning driver.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
