      "description": "Presenting a true automotive time capsule: this vehicle is in showroom-fresh condition, meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero stone chips or imperfections, while the interior retains its original factory scent and supple, untouched leather surfaces. Every electronic component functions flawlessly, and the engine bay is detailed to a professional standard. Accompanied by a complete, documented service history and all original keys, this car drives exactly as it did the day it left the lot. This is an exceptional example for the discerning collector who demands perfection.",
