    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo, preserved in its factory-original configuration. Under the hood lies the legendary 2JZ-GTE inline-six, featuring its original sequential twin-turbocharger setup and an unmolested induction system. The powertrain is mated to the robust Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission, delivering torque through the factory Torsen limited-slip differential. Mechanically, the vehicle is superlative; compression across all six cylinders remains within factory specifications, and the cooling system has been overhauled with OEM components to ensure thermal efficiency. The chassis retains its structural integrity with zero oxidation, and the four-wheel double-wishbone suspension provides the precise lateral kinematics intended by Toyota\u2019s engineers. This specimen features immaculate paint depth and a cockpit free of UV degradation or bolster wear. For the discerning collector seeking peak JDM performance without the typical aftermarket interference.",
